- <i>No no no.</i>

29
00:04:26,468 --> 00:04:29,002
- Shh, shh.
- Oh my god.

30
00:04:29,003 --> 00:04:31,046
<i>Stay with me! Stay with me!</i>

31
00:04:31,047 --> 00:04:32,850
<i>Hey hey hey hey!</i>

32
00:04:32,851 --> 00:04:35,194
Come on, stop struggling.

33
00:04:35,195 --> 00:04:37,961
I can help you.
