35
00:04:41,348 --> 00:04:44,093
- Come over here.
- I want to.

36
00:04:45,857 --> 00:04:49,202
That's it. Come on.

37
00:04:49,203 --> 00:04:52,409
Okay. Oh, yeah.
Oh my god.

38
00:04:52,410 --> 00:04:55,185
- Oh, god.
- What are you looking at?

39
00:04:56,758 --> 00:04:59,594
I was looking at this beautiful
bracelet you got there.

40
