- You want to get something to eat?
- I had lunch.

41
00:05:04,183 --> 00:05:05,791
We could get some ice cream.

42
00:05:05,792 --> 00:05:08,190
- No, I gotta go away.
- What's your hurry?

43
00:05:08,191 --> 00:05:10,194
What's it to you?

44
00:05:10,195 --> 00:05:13,402
I thought maybe we could get
some coffee or something.

45
00:05:13,412 --> 00:05:15,375
No?

46
00:05:15,376 --> 00:05:18,621
Hey, man, why don't you just mind
your own business, all right?

47
00:05:18,622 --> 00:05:21,027
Everything's all right.

48
00:05:23,842 --> 00:05:25,445
Everything's okay, huh?

49
00:05:25,446 --> 00:05:27,449
Come on, don't worry.

50
00:05:27,450 --> 00:05:31,057
Get in the car.
Everything's gonna be okay.

51
00:05:34,504 --> 00:05:36,738
- There you go.
- Thank you.

52
00:05:41,728 --> 00:05:43,731
- You want this one?
- No, thanks.

53
00:05:43,732 --> 00:05:45,865
Well, then...

54
00:05:45,867 --> 00:05:49,813
Which one do I eat first?

55
00:05:49,814 --> 00:05:52,759
- They both look so good, don't they?
- No, not to me.

56
00:05:52,760 --> 00:05:57,368
- You give this much grief to your parents?
- I don't see my parents.

57
00:05:57,369 --> 00:06:00,445
- You don't live at home?
- No, I live on my own.

58
00:06:00,446 --> 00:06:03,892
- I've got my own money.
- How old are you, 14 or 15?

59
00:06:03,893 --> 00:06:06,697
<i>16.</i>

60
00:06:06,698 --> 00:06:09,142
