61
00:06:09,143 --> 00:06:11,146
Stop grilling me.

62
00:06:11,147 --> 00:06:13,050
Stop, okay?

63
00:06:13,051 --> 00:06:15,325
I'm sorry.

64
00:06:18,131 --> 00:06:20,005
It's just that...

65
00:06:22,009 --> 00:06:24,414
I used to have some track
marks like that myself.

66
00:06:24,424 --> 00:06:26,438
You don't
know anything about me.

67
00:06:26,439 --> 00:06:30,034
- Yes, I do.
- No, you don't.

68
00:06:30,035 --> 00:06:32,409
If you've got a drug
problem, I can help you out.

69
00:06:32,410 --> 00:06:35,816
I don't have a problem with drugs.
I just...

70
00:06:47,259 --> 00:06:49,663
Are you happy? Hmm?

71
00:06:49,664 --> 00:06:52,168
