00:19:18,601 --> 00:19:21,816
on that tour de France item.
Go with that.

221
00:19:21,817 --> 00:19:25,654
- I am <i>not going on in front of this.
- Welcome back, grace.</i>

222
00:19:25,655 --> 00:19:29,702
Can't we go with something
a little more stylized?

223
00:19:29,703 --> 00:19:32,007
