not finished yet.

224
00:19:32,008 --> 00:19:34,081
- Oh, much better.
- No, that is not better.

225
00:19:34,082 --> 00:19:36,086
I'd prefer just plain type.

226
00:19:36,096 --> 00:19:38,105
Maybe something
like "headhunter."

227
00:19:38,106 --> 00:19:40,064
- Perfect, great idea.
- Keep it tasteful.

228
00:19:41,076 --> 00:19:43,079
I have to get back.

229
00:19:43,080 --> 00:19:46,686
Ben needs me to rehearse
some of his ad libs.

230
00:19:51,507 --> 00:19:54,612
Hey, grace, that is
a fabulous outfit on you.

231
00:19:54,613 --> 00:19:56,516
I know what to give her.

232
00:19:56,517 --> 00:19:59,623
<i>- What?
- Big blood-red letters.</i>

233
00:19:59,633 --> 00:20:02,108
Three feet high.

234
00:20:07,318 --> 00:20:09,722
Hello.

235
00:20:09,723 --> 00:20:12,127
Yes, it is.

236
00:20:12,128 --> 00:20:14,873
Of course I want it back.
Where the hell are you?

237
00:20:17,519 --> 00:20:19,822
I only took $6.

238
00:20:19,823 --> 00:20:22,227
I... I needed some food.

239
00:20:22,228 --> 00:20:24,502
I've been wandering
around since last night.

240
00:20:24,503 --> 00:20:28,209
- How'd you find me?
- Your I.D. Card.

241
00:20:28,210 --> 00:20:30,515
I tried your home first.

242
00:20:30,525 --> 00:20:32,539
You haven't got any place to go?

243
00:20:32,540 --> 00:20:36,205
- No.
- You looking for a place to stay?

244
00:20:36,206 --> 00:20:39,482
No. I need something else.

245
00:20:39,483 --> 00:20:41,886
You kept trying to help me,

246
00:20:41,887 --> 00:20:44,161
so I thought...

247
00:20:44,162 --> 00:20:46,797
- Okay, so you need some more money.
- <i>No.</i>

